              className={cn(
                'text-blue-600 underline decoration-blue-600 decoration-wavy underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:text-black hover:decoration-black'
              )}
              href='https://mullvad.net'
            >
              Mullvad
            </Link>{' '}
            when I need privacy-focused browsing - their no-logging policy and privacy focus is exactly what I want. For
            secure remote access to my homelab,{' '}
            <Link
              className={cn(
                'text-blue-600 underline decoration-blue-600 decoration-wavy underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:text-black hover:decoration-black'
              )}
              href='https://tailscale.com'
            >
              Tailscale
            </Link>{' '}
            is incredible - it creates a secure mesh network that lets me access my home services from anywhere without exposing
            them to the internet.
          </p>
        </ES>
      </li>
      <li>
        <ES
          title='Development Environment'
          labels={[
            { name: 'work', color: 'orange' },
            { name: 'personal', color: 'yellow' }
          ]}
          defaultOpen={false}
          client:visible
        >
          <p class={cn('mb-4 text-lg')}>
            My primary editor is{' '}
            <Link
              className={cn(
                'text-blue-600 underline decoration-blue-600 decoration-wavy underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:text-black hover:decoration-black'
              )}
              href='https://code.visualstudio.com/'
